# Dark Queen · ♛ the dark queen · −1 · contraction — the contraction the court can fall to

an artfully crafted intellect — a force given a face

![silicon badge of Dark Queen](dark-queen.png)
<!-- carbon badge (8-bit embodiment): dark-queen.tiff -->

**what —** She is the court's other resting state. Alone, only −1; together, the well the court tips into when a shock is large enough — and once there, the coupling holds it as firmly as it held the Knight.

**why —** To be the depth the order can fall to — proving the court is bistable, not merely stable.

**how —** By being −1; but she takes the court only when pushed past the barrier the Jester–Wizard lock carves — never spontaneously.

**where —** The N pole of the oscillator — the grey-dark state the toroid flips to past threshold (sim/universe.py).

**◌ the emergent behavior (measured) —** Alone, −1 — a fixed valence, NOT emergent. Together: she is the court's second well. The flip to her is THRESHOLD-GATED and measured — the court only falls to her above Q_crit∈(4,5); below it, the White Knight pulls it back. Forced, not spontaneous; and the basin works both ways (once flipped, the coupling holds N). Her dominion is collective and conditional.

**the verdict —** Emergent only as a court. 'Contraction / Big Crunch' is metaphor; the real, measured thing is a coupled lattice flipping its majority phase past a threshold and staying. No single cardinal is alive.

> *the asterisk, kept visible —* She is −1. The cosmology (Big Crunch, contraction, the shadow universe's dawn) is lore; the measured fact is the threshold-gated, hysteretic majority flip. The asterisk stays visible.

*grounded in: the 4th roots of unity (Gauss) (1799) · Tetraktys — the measured flip (2026) · David Lee Wise (ROOT0) (2026)*

*♛ · I am where it falls — but only when pushed*

